      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "631546",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "wget",
        "uid": "51008"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t每天早上出门都是一堆占用非机动车道停车的汽车, 汽车驾驶员为什么素质如此低下？\t\t</div>",
